雨。雨停之后，我们就各自回家了。什么？要找我女朋友？别开玩笑了，我们才认识两个小时，连手机号我都没问呢。什么彩虹我没看见，反正什么事我都没做。”\r<br>彩虹，教堂，阳光……\r<br>夜羽，夕恋嘴角微微向上扬起。\r<br>“犯人就是你！”&nbsp;夕恋把手指向嫌疑犯B。\r<br>嫌疑犯B一楞，反问夕恋：“为什么？”\r<br>夜羽说：“当时，我和夕恋在餐厅吃饭，我们吃饭的餐厅正对着东西走向的马路，可以把彩虹一览无余，说明彩虹的走向也是东西的&nbsp;。”\r<br>夕恋接着说：“下午5点30分的时候，太阳应该是偏西的，如果你在教堂前&nbsp;，应该是正方向&nbsp;即正南北，&nbsp;才能看到彩虹&nbsp;，不可能被阳光刺痛眼睛&nbsp;，所以你在说谎。”\r<br>说时迟，那时快，嫌疑犯B跑了，很快不见人影了。\r<br>等到夜羽，夕恋追到嫌疑犯B时，嫌疑犯B早已不省人事了。\r<br>—————————————NO.3完———————————————\u0018","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-25 13:01","ip":null,"old_image":"http://hiphotos.baidu.com/lovedepplove/pic/item/8aee034ee6203bc7d0c86a55.jpg","user_sign_image":null},{"index":99,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】魔法侦探社","content":"绫子，我都懒得看来真的~但对不起你额。。。\r<br>于是帮你UP下下~","author":"伊凌雪love帅蒙","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.a5ff5a89.HNHZsxoDeyjJbS6DTwthJA&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-25 13:04","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":100,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】魔法侦探社","content":"UP~","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-25 21:45","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":101,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】魔法侦探社","content":"UP~","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-26 00:14","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":102,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】魔法侦探社","content":"闪人~","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-26 00:17","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":103,"title":"回复：回复：【原创】魔法侦探社","content":"UP~","author":"江户川绫子","author_link":"https://tieba.baidu.com/home/main?id=tb.1.574b664c.30cDok9HldwodkqdCIvGsQ&fr=pb","date":"2009-01-26 08:24","ip":null,"old_image":null,"user_sign_image":null},{"index":104,"title":"回